===Etymology===
Middle English and Middle French ''[[sillabe]]'' < {{etyl|la}} {{term|syllaba|lang=la}} < {{etyl|grc}} {{term|συλλαβή||sc=Polytonic|tr=sullabē|lang=grc}} < {{term|συλλαμβάνω||I gather together|sc=Polytonic|tr=sullambanō|lang=grc}} < {{term|συν|συν-|together|sc=Polytonic|tr=sun-|lang=grc}} + {{term|λαμβάνω||I take|tr=lambanō|lang=grc|sc=polytonic}}.

===Pronunciation===
